        "excerpt": "Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                              Dirge of Doom                  Novice                                                                                                             Dispiriting Taunt                  Novice                                                                                                             Inspire Courage                  Novice                                                                                                             Inspire Heroics                  Veteran                                                                                     Unity                  Veteran                                                                                                             Soothing Ballad                  Master                                                                                                             Fatal Performance                  Epic                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        Tier Bonuses                                                                                 Dirge of Doom                              Novice                                       Composition                    Emotion                    Fear                    Mental                                                      Area           30-foot emanation                    Duration           1 round                                  Foes within the area are frightened 1. They can’t reduce their frightened value below 1 while they remain in the area.                                  Dispiriting Taunt                              Novice                                       Auditory                    Emotion                    Fear                    Linguistic                    Mental                                                      Range           60 feet                    Duration           1 round                                  Make an Intimidate roll against the target’s Will DC.                                   Critical Success           As success, and the target is stunned 1                             Success           The target has a -2 penalty to all die rolls                             Failure           The target has a -2 penalty to attack rolls                                                        Inspire Courage                              Novice                                       Composition                    Emotion                    Mental                                                      Area           60-foot emanation                    Duration           1 round                                  You inspire your allies with words or tunes of encouragement. You and all allies in the area gain one of the following benefits:     +1 bonus to attack rolls, damage rolls, and saves against Fear effects   +1 bonus to AC and saving throws, as well as resistance to physical damage equal to your Envoy level   +10-foot bonus to Speed                                  Inspire Heroics              Veteran                                             Prerequisites           Inspire Courage                                  The bonuses granted by Inspire Courage are doubled.                                  Unity                              Veteran                                       Fortune                                                      Trigger           You and 1 or more allies within range are targeted by a spell or ability that allows a saving throw                    Range           30 feet                    Targets           Each ally targeted by the triggering spell                                  You put up a united defense. Each ally can use your saving throw modifier instead of its own against the triggering spell. Each ally decides individually which modifier to use.                                  Soothing Ballad                              Master                                       Composition                    Emotion                    Healing                    Mental                                                      Range           30 feet                    Targets           You and up to 9 allies                                  You draw upon your muse to soothe your allies. Choose one of the following three effects:     Disrupt all Fear effects on the targets   Disrupt all effects causing the paralyzed condition on the targets   Restore 7d8 HP to the targets                                  Fatal Performance                              Epic                                       Composition                    Death                    Emotion                    Encounter                    Mental                                                      Range           30 feet                                  Your performance is so perfect that the target may die of joy or sorrow. The target takes 50 damage. If this brings it to 0 HP, it dies instantly.",
